      • Builder

        public Builder(String accessToken)
        Create a new GetCurrentUsersRecentlyPlayedTracksRequest.Builder.

        Your access token must have the user-read-recently-played scope authorized in order to read the user's recently played track.

        Parameters:
        accessToken - Required. A valid access token from the Spotify Accounts service.
        See Also:
        Spotify: Using Scopes
